Company.

 

(d)          Except
as set forth in Schedule 2.3(d) , no outstanding Company
Common Shares are unvested or subjected to a repurchase option,
risk of forfeiture or other condition under any applicable
agreement with the Company

 

(e)           The
common share of the Company to be issued by the Company to Holdco
in connection with the Transaction Merger, upon issuance in
