notes thereto) of the Company for the fiscal years ended December
31, 2013 and 2012 (the “ Audited Financial Statements
”). The Audited Financial Statements were prepared in
accordance with generally accepted accounting principles of the
United States (“ U.S. GAAP ”) applied on a
consistent basis throughout the periods involved (except as may be
indicated in the notes thereto), and each fairly presents in all
